(58380, 'AD2BF071-2352-4FAA-9839-98329DDDBBF9', 'This is a bit out of sequence…as I wrote before I got off the ground but got stuck on my phone….just landed.  I am so sorry for making you feel beat down and “pummeled” …trying to repeatedly, forcefully, harshly convince you of why I am right and why you are wrong.  Trying to push you to change even after you made it very clear that you have reached your own truth and bottom line. Making you feel unloved and broken. For scaring you in the car and other times, making you feel unsafe. For not being able to hear you and support you when you made it clear how desperate and hopeless and alone you have been feeling. I have my own pain from you and your actions and words from the last 2 months. But I can put that aside for now and work through slowly, when we are in a better space with the support  of Priscilla.  I accept your decision and will continue  to work through my feelings in order to minimize the impact on our connection and intimacy. I know I can count on and will need your help here.  I love you dearly.  I want you to feel at home again, wrapped in my arms.  ', '688440432637008384', 'None', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'E:nwdave@b-zb.com', 'David', '2022-10-25T18:27:12.637008'),
